[64]National Security Agency chief fired as Trump ousts another top military
officer

   [65]April 4, 2025  Air Force Gen. Timothy Haugh served just over a
   year as director of the NSA, the spy agency that collects cyber
   intelligence worldwide. He's the latest of several senior officers
   fired by Trump.

