[141]Consider This from NPR

[142]The fallout from the Signal breach begins

   [143]March 25, 2025  In the 24 hours since a bombshell Atlantic
   article, senators have grilled Trump administration intelligence
   officials — but there are no signs yet that anyone involved will face
   any repercussions. The article, by Jeffrey Goldberg, details how he was
   inadvertently added to a chat on Signal, the encrypted messaging app,
   where key administration figures were planning a U.S. bombing operation
   in Yemen.

The fallout from the Signal breach begins

